                      String assignmentRef,

                      String updateRemoveSubmission,

        integration with gradebook
        Parameters:
        state -
        assignmentRef - Assignment reference
        associateGradebookAssignment - The title for the associated GB assignment
        addUpdateRemoveAssignment - "add" for adding the assignment; "update" for updating the assignment; "remove" for remove assignment
        oldAssignment_title - The original assignment title
        newAssignment_title - The updated assignment title
        newAssignment_maxPoints - The maximum point of the assignment
        newAssignment_dueTime - The due time of the assignment
        submissionRef - Any submission grade need to be updated? Do bulk update if null
        updateRemoveSubmission - "update" for update submission;"remove" for remove submission
